data.description: Assumable VA Loan at 2.5%. Discover your dream home in the heart of Arbuckle, with easy access to the Highway. One of the biggest floor plan in Honey grove community. This home boasts 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 2 car garage, owned solar and beautifully landscaped front and backyard. 1 bedroom and 1 full bathroom on the 1st floor. Updated home with stylish flooring and granite counter tops. Spacious interiors with an open family room and kitchen combo, formal dinning room, and a loft to use for movie room or play area or office for your work from home set-up. The private backyard is a peaceful oasis, perfect for outdoor dining, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day. Long and expanded driveway to park multiple vehicles or RV/Boat. Close to the community walking trails, golf course, parks and school. Big and beautiful home with Low water and sewer fees, and low pge bills - what else can you ask for?
